room_title: Escape room "Space Station Escape (VR)" by Riddles Escape Room in Myrtle Beach
room_address: 9713 N. Kings Highway Myrtle Beach, SC 29577
room_description:
Step into a new realm of space travel as you enter this fantasy galaxy and wake up in a futuristic body on the Eden Space Station. Work as a team using the highest technology to escape. Your hand movements will complete tasks and puzzles, move objects, and expect to FLY!
This is a Virtual Reality escape room.
